  <text>
    <body>
      <div xml:id="Romans" n="B05" type="Epistle">
        <div type="rubric" corresp="Ro1:1">
          <pb source="#S155" n="39r" facs="http://localhost:8000/sinai/ark%3A%2F21198%2Fz1bs09w9%2F2t41720x/full/1500,/0/default.jpg" />
          <head xml:lang="ar" rend="red decorated">
            <l>نبدا نكتب مصحف بولس الرسول الصحيفه الولا</l>
            <l>كتبها الي اهل روميه باسم ربنا المسيح</l>
          </head>
          <note type="translation" xml:lang="en">
            We begin to write the Book of Paul the Apostle, the first Epistle,
            which he wrote to the people of Rome. In the name of our Lord Christ.
          </note>
        </div>
        <div type="rubric" corresp="Ro5:1">
          <pb source="#S155" n="43v" facs="http://127.0.0.1:8000/sinai/ark%3A%2F21198%2Fz1bs09w9%2F4k04d71t/full/1500,/0/default.jpg" />
          <head xml:lang="ar" rend="red">
            <l>تقرا في الاحد الاول هذه اول القرايات</l>
          </head>
          <note type="translation" xml:lang="en">
            It is read on the <date when-custom="#Pent1Sun">first Sunday</date>. This is the first reading.
          </note>
        </div>
        <div type="rubric" corresp="Ro6:3">
          <pb source="#S155" n="44v" facs="http://127.0.0.1:8000/sinai/ark%3A%2F21198%2Fz1bs09w9%2Fjq16dv05/full/1500,/0/default.jpg"/>
          <head xml:lang="ar" rend="red">
            <l>تقرا في الاحد الثاني</l>
          </head>
          <note type="translation" xml:lang="en">
            It is read on the <date when-custom="#Pent2Sun">second Sunday</date>.
          </note>
        </div>
        <div type="rubric" corresp="Ro8:2">
          <pb source="#S155" n="46v" facs="http://127.0.0.1:8000/sinai/ark%3A%2F21198%2Fz1bs09w9%2F4357gf3p/full/1500,/0/default.jpg"/>
          <head xml:lang="ar" rend="red">
            <l>تقرا في الاحد الثالث</l>
          </head>
          <note type="translation" xml:lang="en">
            It is read on the <date when-custom="#Pent3Sun">third Sunday</date>.
          </note>
        </div>
        <div type="rubric" corresp="Ro8:28">
          <pb source="#S155" n="47v" facs="http://127.0.0.1:8000/sinai/ark%3A%2F21198%2Fz1bs09w9%2F7x46h90v/full/1500,/0/default.jpg"/>
          <head xml:lang="ar" rend="red">
            <l>
              <w>في</w>
              <hi rend="strikethrough">لا</hi>
              <w>عياد</w>
              <w>الشهدا</w>
            </l>
          </head>
          <note type="translation" xml:lang="en">
            On the <date when-custom="#Martyrs">Feasts of the Martyrs</date>.
          </note>
        </div>
        <div type="rubric" corresp="Ro9:30">
          <pb source="#S155" n="49r" facs="http://127.0.0.1:8000/sinai/ark%3A%2F21198%2Fz1bs09w9%2Fk316pd3k/full/1500,/0/default.jpg"/>
          <head xml:lang="ar" rend="red">
            <l>
              <w>تقرا</w>
              <w>في</w>
              <w>الاحد</w>
              <w>الرابع</w>
            </l>
          </head>
          <note type="translation" xml:lang="en">
            It is read on the <date when-custom="#Pent4Sun">fourth Sunday</date>.
          </note>
        </div>

      </div><!-- Romans -->
    </body>
  </text>
